===Noun===
'''brucellosis''' (''plural:'' '''[[brucelloses]]''')
# {{pathology}} Infection by the [[bacterium]], [[Brucella]], which is carried by [[ruminant]]s. Symptoms include fevers, sweating, weakness, [[anorexia]], [[headache]]s, [[depression]] and generalized aches and pains.

